entry.title: Ukrainian Forces Repel Russian Attack on Kyiv
entry.content: Thousands of civilians take up arms to help defend the capital, while Russian forces face fierce resistance throughout Ukraine.

entry.title: Ordinary Ukrainians Rally to Defend Homeland From Russia
entry.content: Thousands of Ukrainian civilian fighters volunteer their service, including many from abroad, as authorities in Kyiv distribute rifles and others assemble Molotov cocktails and coordinate support.

entry.title: Russia's Energy Dominance Ties West's Hands in Ukraine War
entry.content: Europe gets about 40% of its natural-gas imports from Russia, making it hard to sanction a sector that is a vital source of revenue for Moscow.
